      • removeDockerContainer

        @GET
 @Path(value="docker/remove")
public javax.ws.rs.core.Response removeDockerContainer(@QueryParam(value="imageName")
                                                                                          java.lang.String imageName,
                                                                                          @QueryParam(value="removeFiles")
                                                                                          ChronixBoolean removeFiles)
        Removes all docker containers related to imageName. If removeFiles is selected, removes the image with imageName and the related files.
        Parameters:
        imageName - the image name
        removeFiles - "yes", "true" or "y" to delete image and all files.
        Returns:
        the server response with server cli output in entity as String[].
